{"tid":337088,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"印度雜誌封面印中國地圖　刪除台灣西藏","createTime":"2017-07-27T03:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T02:00:58.000Z","uid":53947,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd2422e3b2b3cebcbebdde0c8ed5d661641755f","tid":337088,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:59:27.000Z","msg":"有些外媒或國家媒體在談及中國版圖領土的時候，會「不經意」地把台灣也畫進去。但印度雜誌《今日印度》在最新一期雜誌中，就把台灣和西藏從中國版圖中剔除，更形容中國是一隻「雞」，正帶領著巴基斯坦這隻「小雞」。<br />\n<br />\n《今日印度》這期雜誌的封面故事，闡述中國不斷對巴基斯坦砸下銀彈攻勢，來提升兩國友誼，並帶領著巴基斯坦這隻「小雞」，來圍攻印度，並呼籲印度政府應該要有所警覺。但這樣的封面看在中國媒體的眼裡，《新浪網》就直呼：「我們的西藏、台灣呢？！ 故意從中國版圖中刪除西藏、台灣，《今日印度》想表達什麼呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此外，《今日印度》還稱這期封面因設計獨特，受到美國出版設計師協會(SPD)的青睞，被選為「當日最佳封面」。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qz9bvt40\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqz9bvt40&h=81fc07fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22bb06ff4c78de5a8e2bead3374a76a1efbd544c","tid":337088,"uid":53672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:01:33.000Z","msg":"咖哩仔都咁串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a24ac1b087b186d6d0a3d59e006e2d068d1db95","tid":337088,"uid":66514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:05:56.000Z","msg":"good job"},{"pid":"dfa40636bd3d41cfa78c51bd9db2e204a96fbfbd","tid":337088,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:09:08.000Z","msg":"唔好干預人地內政啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4564bddab16647828d82409ca3c7b32b50fd52d2","tid":337088,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"a1568412bde35e4c37256f2bf2dbba6b98322dc0","tid":337088,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:13:16.000Z","msg":"新疆 青海 香港 都要刪埋啦<br />\n<br />\n印度佬做野真係那西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48df113